  <h2>Crafting</h2>
  <text>Silicon wafers are produced by cutting <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/silicon_boule" underlined="true">Monocrystalline Silicon Boules</style> in an at lowest MV-Tier voltage <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/cutter" underlined="true">cutter</style>.</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_silicon_boule_water"></recipe>
  <text>Later wafers, namely the phosphorus, naquadah and neutronium ones can be produced in a similar matter, although with higher voltage (HV, EV and IV respectively) and in a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:multiblock/cleanroom" underlined="true">Cleanroom</style>.</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_phosphorus_boule_water"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_naquadah_boule_water"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:cutter/cut_neutronium_boule_water"></recipe>
  <br></br>
  <h2>Usage</h2>
  <text left-margin="10">- 1 EU/t <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:covers/solar_panel" underlined="true">Solar Panel</style>;</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:shaped/solar_panel_basic"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:shaped/solar_panel_ulv"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:shaped/solar_panel_lv"></recipe>
  <br></br>
  <text left-margin="10">- <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:covers/solar_panel" underlined="true">Diode</style>;</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:assembler/diode_polyethylene_wafer"></recipe>
  <br></br>
  <h2>Engraving</h2>
  <text left-margin="10">Them main purpose of wafers is to be engraved in a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/laser_engraver" underlined="true">Laser Engraver</style>, these engraved wafers can then be cut to components to be used for creating circuits. The recipes shown here show the lowest tier wafer needed to make an engraved wafer, higher tier wafers can be used and produce 4, 8 and 16 times the normal output for 1, 2 or 3 tiers above required respectively. Engraving any wafers above silicon requires a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:multiblock/cleanroom" underlined="true">Cleanroom</style>.</text>
  <recipe id="gtceu:laser_engraver/engrave_ulpic_silicon"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:laser_engraver/engrave_ssoc_silicon"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:laser_engraver/engrave_ram_silicon"></recipe>
  <recipe id="gtceu:laser_engraver/engrave_lpic_silicon"></recipe>
